marketing: Pennzoil^® Motor Oil with Active Cleansing Technology. Helps prevent dirt and contaminants from turning into performance robbing deposits. Because at Pennzoil^® we know, a cleaner engine is better protected and responsive. It meets or exceeds the engine protection required by API SN, and is specially formulated to provide proven wear protection.
